Program: Discovery
Title: Samuel Ting of CERN
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrxh8
Last Broadcast Date: 16 September 1999
An interview with Nobel Prize winning physicist Samuel Ting of CERN. The scientist who has made an enormous impact on the world of particle physics, talks about his work in the huge particle accelerator under the Franco-Swiss border.